{"tid":1449241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:36.000Z","uid":114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2b5b0853f16dba6fa17b099454b4facd8d4944da","tid":1449241,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=671ac2e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n<br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=bc212fab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"e829f6e8a8e6a91bdc75bb96e4dcd7034f781753","tid":1449241,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d79bc07dacfd695ba64a441e762f0821dd9c60","tid":1449241,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cf6a5bf5b2c42dcb01a2d9ee61b1f59810b7a1","tid":1449241,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c9cf85f641a92b599290214b97e6107d44f7cf","tid":1449241,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor